snippet.title: Swift: YouTube - MVC Explained: Model View Controller (Ep 4)
snippet.description:
Let's go over one of the most common design patterns we see in iOS development: MVC.  So far we've been writing all of our code in views and controllers, so now lets complete the implementation by writing our model objects. We'll create video and channel models to continue making progress in our YouTube application.
